      "description": "For sale is a reliable vehicle in good overall condition. The exterior retains a strong shine, though there are a few minor stone chips on the hood and a small scuff on the rear bumper from normal use. Inside, the cabin is clean and well-preserved, with all electronics, climate control, and infotainment features functioning perfectly. It has been regularly serviced, and the engine runs smoothly with no known mechanical issues. This car is ready for a new owner who values a well-maintained, dependable ride.",
