      "description": "Hey there! You have seriously got to see this beauty. It's honestly like it just rolled off the showroom floor\u2014not a single scratch or dent anywhere! I've babied this car from day one, keeping it tucked away in the garage and staying on top of every little service detail. It drives like an absolute dream and still has that wonderful new-car smell. I'm really sad to see it go, but I know the next owner is going to be over the moon with it. Come by and take a look for yourself!",
